{"id":263691,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-成都访民维权「简报」第二十四期（2012·11·1/","date":"2012-11-18T07:15:38Z","modified":"2012-11-18T07:15:38Z","title":"维权网 | 成都访民维权「简报」第二十四期（2012·11·1﹣11·15）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>宗旨：给政府提供维稳线索；留下访民辛酸足迹（冰山一角）</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>，锦江区强拆访民李廷惠被便衣从家楼下被带走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>被宣布行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>天，理由是所谓的非法上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区强拆访民岳中顺、岳中芳到省国土资源厅上访，由金处长接待。金处长说，我已与青羊区政府、交通局督促协调多次，，他们不解决，我也没办法。我带你们见黄欣初书记。后来金处长又没胆量带访民去。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>，锦江区强拆访民周成群被带到当地派出所，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>被宣布行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>天，理由是所谓的非法上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>，锦江区强拆访民郭玉彬被带到当地派出所，被宣布行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>天，理由是所谓的非法上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>锦江芷同桥正街</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">75</span><span>赖根龙进京上访，国家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">211</span><span>接待员，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>号回到成都。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>，温江出租车维权代表毛留成被跟踪。据悉他爱人北京上访后回来后即被刑事拘留，一月后宣布逮捕。至今无下文。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>，锦江区强拆访民周成群，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>被宣布行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>天，理由是所谓的非法上访。由于父亲突然逝世，经她家属申请，行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>天改为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区强拆访民岳中顺、岳中芳、廖西联、杨邦惠、孙玉、李俊、李发俊、李泉玉到市国土资源上访，由彭健辉书记接待，他说，访民的问题已解决，赔偿已赔够了的。农村的房子想拆就拆，想赔多少就赔多少，可以不按政策文件。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>，成都成华万年办事处访民洪英按办事处电话通知要求到街道办谈她家房子将被不公平强拆之事，她到街道办后，街道办说没通知。下午，街道办又带纸条给她，让她</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日到街道办谈拆迁之事。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，崇州羊马镇政府非法圈地，村民阻挡，结果被逮捕十几人，后当地警方正式刑事拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>人。至今无音讯。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，成都青羊区文家访民何艾芩被当地治保主任黄健带队的四个大汉打倒病在床上。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，成都成华万年办事处访民洪英按办事处通知要求到街道办谈她家房子将被不公平强拆之事（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">05</span><span>年拆迁签字前被不明人员暴打后被迫签字），她到街道办后，她阐述了自己的诉求，然政府仍坚持原处理决定。谈判破裂，政府宣布明天对她家强拆。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，成都温江区有关当轴安排川</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">AW 3M 98</span><span>民用车紧紧跟踪温江出租车维权访民，从温江到成都，从成都又回到温江。期间，出租车维权访民多次试图摆脱跟踪都没有成功。跟踪人员还对出租车维权访民的所有活动拍照摄像。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，成都锦江强拆访民邓品芳从成都出发，进京上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日赶到北京。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区强拆访民岳中顺、岳中芳、廖西联、杨邦惠、孙玉、李俊、李发俊、李泉玉到青羊去信访办上访，由李书记接待。他叫来交通局吴姓工程师将他们接到交通局。去后没任何说法，又被街道办接到武侯区清水河公园喝茶吃饭后没任何说法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>，成都访民与维权人士相约到成都安靖拘留所看望李廷惠、郭玉彬。由于访民没经验，只有维权人士陈先生见了李廷惠与郭玉彬。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>，街道办社区三次找到青羊区强拆访民岳中顺、岳中芳、孙玉、李俊、李发俊、李泉玉接到武侯区清水河公园喝茶吃饭后没任何说法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>，成都成华万年办事处访民洪英家房子，由办事处喊来</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多人强拆除。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区文家强拆访民李华成约到区信访办，要求他在区政府解决部分问题后息诉息访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，成都六四遇难者母亲唐德英发现又人对她监控后，她大胆地对他们指责。之后几天，监控人没再出现。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>号，青羊区强拆访民岳中顺、岳中芳被约王主任到街道办，街道办将他们的诉求做了个总结。后他表态，叫访民不要伸张，他去协调土地补偿</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>万元，房子拆了算了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区苏坡强拆访民廖西联、杨邦惠到市政府上访，廖西联被街道办几个人员强制拖二三百米，衣服被拖烂，还威胁要收拾她。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>，都江堰访民李绣被截访后送到马家楼。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>号被送回成都。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>午后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>，康凤群从国务院信访局、人大、中纪委上访出来，走到陶然桥</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">106</span><span>路公交站被北京警察带上警车。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>过，成都青羊区强拆访民刘存钦进京上访被截访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>，成都锦江区强拆访民邓品芳被截访回成都。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>，四川西充县人民医院</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5?12</span><span>香港援建项目，材料供应商何琼、冯来如、张传林等五人到公安厅上访。向督察大队投诉当地警察施暴问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>，成都六四遇难者母亲唐德英发现，离她家不远又有一辆车四五人对她实行监控。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>，新都新繁强拆访民景永江诉讼案在新都法院开庭。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区强拆访民岳中顺、岳中芳先到交通局，再到去政府上访，没有人接待。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>，青羊区文家强拆访民李华成到青羊区政府上访，政府拒绝接待。他坚持等到下午才接待，组织部长接待，他说成都试验区不按规定有行先试的权利，你不要以为你多学了些法想多赔是不可能的。随你怎么办就等于零。接待无结果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>，成都青羊区强拆访民刘存钦进京上访被截访送回成都后，至今无下落。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分，成都宽窄巷子血拆访民王蓉文因为十八大闭幕，被旅游从西昌市回到井巷子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>号的“家”中。从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>早晨的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分王蓉文出大门，被青羊区少城街办综治办主任李双全为首的综治办王坚、段亚萍带走旅游，共计</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">49</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">32</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分，彭天慧母亲在锦江区科甲巷的房屋强拆迁案在成都中院第十法庭开庭，代理人是其儿子彭耀武。阚思云、邓品芳、赖蓉、张玉珍、张达敏、罗民方等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>多位旁听。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>「遗漏补充」：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>，青羊区文家强拆访民李华成进京上访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>号到京。到国务院信访办上访后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日被截访送回。同天他还收到北京市公安局西城区公安分局府右街派出所的训诫书。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>「更正」：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、上期</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>条“…新都新繁强拆访民收到法院传票…”更正为“…新都新繁强拆访民景永江收到法院传票…”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-6107077872139707188?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}